Background

		Mr. Robyn W. Peterson serves as the Chief Technology Officer and Head of Product at Mashable, Inc. Mr. Peterson oversees product strategy and the technical direction of Mashable. He serves as an Advisor of Parsely, Inc. He served as Senior Vice President of Product at Mashable, Inc., since joining in May 2011. Before joining Mashable, he served as the Head of Product at Next Issue Media. His previous roles include Vice President of Technology and Product at NBC Universal, ... Senior Vice President of Product Management and Chief Technology Officer at Ziff Davis Media and Director of Operations at Juno. He has been instrumental in launching some of the most interesting media products of the past 10 years. He served as Vice President for Technology and Product for NBCUniversal. He has been an Independent Director of World Wrestling Entertainment Inc., since February 2015. Mr. Peterson received his Bachelor of Arts from the University of Wisconsin at Madison and his Master’s Degree in Computer Science from New York University.Read Full Background




